name: Artwork 2 (Dreams and Nightmares)
description: Image of MLK during his famous “I have a dream” speech. Writing on the artwork says “I have a dream… that one day this nation will rise up and live out the true meaning of its creed: “We hold these truths to be self evident, that all men are created equal”. But why is this a nightmare to so many people?”. If you choose to buy this item I will sent you the full version and without the yellow writing via email.
